{{Infobox International Football Competition | tourney_name = | year = | other_titles = | image = | size = | caption = | country = United Arab Emirates | dates = 15 March &ndash; 22 March | num_teams = 4 | confederations = 1 | venues = 1 | cities = 1 | champion_other = {{flagicon|CHN}} [[China PR national under-19 football team|China PR]] | count = 1 | matches = 6 | goals = 25 | attendance = | top_scorer = | player = | prevseason = [[1982 AFC Youth Championship|1982]] | nextseason = [[1986 AFC Youth Championship|1986]] }}
The [[Asian Football Confederation]]'s '''1985 [[AFC Youth Championship]]''' was held in March, 1985 in [[Abu Dhabi]], [[United Arab Emirates]]. The tournament was won by for the first time by [[China national under-20 football team|China PR]] in the final tournaments in round-robin format.
