The '''Cyprus Cycling Federation (CCF)''' ([[Greek language|Greek]]: Κυπριακή Ομοσπονδία Ποδηλασίας, Κ.Ο.ΠΟ) is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Cyprus]].

The CCF is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

